<p>
  <%= @invite.user.username %> has invited you to join DreamTagger.
</p>

<p>
  DreamTagger allows you to record and <b>share your dreams</b> with your friends and the rest
  of the world. By adding tags to your dreams (and other people's dreams!) you can help to create a
  <b>network of dreams</b> based on what they are about.
</p>

<% unless @invite.message.blank? %>
  <p><%= @invite.user.username %> sent the following message:</p>
  <blockquote>
  <%= h @invite.message %>
  </blockquote>
<% end %>

<p>
  To accept the invitation and get started, follow the link below to create an account:
  <br/>
  <%= new_account_url %>
</p>

<p>
  You can find out more about DreamTagger here:
  <br/>
  <%= about_url %>
</p>
